WEBVTT

00:00:01.071 --> 00:00:04.015
I never planned to become
a climate activist.

00:00:04.579 --> 00:00:06.844
But things have changed,

00:00:06.868 --> 00:00:09.928
and now, standing here
as a climate activist,

00:00:09.952 --> 00:00:12.308
I ask you all to become one, too.

00:00:13.193 --> 00:00:14.690
Here's why,

00:00:14.714 --> 00:00:16.868
and most importantly, how.

00:00:18.821 --> 00:00:22.312
Ten years ago, when I was 13 years old,

00:00:22.336 --> 00:00:24.935
I first learned about
the greenhouse effect.

00:00:25.887 --> 00:00:29.705
Back then, we spent
90 minutes on this issue,

00:00:29.729 --> 00:00:31.865
